    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day I first got it. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
