    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, without exaggeration, the finest example of this model currently on the market. Always garaged under a breathable car cover and never driven in inclement weather, the exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory shine, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma, with zero bolster wear, scuffs, or creasing on the seats. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment suite to the high-fidelity premium surround sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous, documented service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a pampered, flawless piece of automotive excellence.",
